OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports News Correspondent
OL,7,FAnn O'Connor visits the Royal Preston
OL,8,Fhospital in Lancashire.
OL,10,FA hospital has launched a new scheme
OL,11,Fto get patients home faster - in an
OL,12,Fattempt to help ease winter pressures.
OL,14,FNew NHS figures shows so-called 'bed
OL,15,Fblocking' in hospitals costs the
OL,16,Fservice more than #200 million a month
OL,17,F- with the North West is one of the
OL,18,Fworst affected regions.
