OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FBed blocking refers to when patients
OL,7,Fare medically fit to leave treatment
OL,8,Fbut don't have ongoing care to go to.
OL,10,FBut now the Royal Preston hospital,
OL,11,FLancashire, which has around 80
OL,12,Fpatients at one time who are at a
OL,13,Fstandstill, says it is determined to
OL,14,Fhelp get more home and back into the
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
