OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FMichael Stewart, an emergency medicine
OL,7,Fconsultant at the hospital explained:
OL,8,F"What happens at the backdoor of the
OL,9,Fhospital - getting patients out,
OL,10,Fgetting patients home - has got a big
OL,11,Fimpact on what we do for the acutely
OL,12,Fill patients coming in the front door."
OL,14,FIt is a scheme which is already
OL,15,Fproving successful - 84-year-old
OL,16,FErnest Turner arrived at the hospital
OL,17,Fwith breathing problems, and fluid on
OL,18,Fhis lungs, but swift treatment meant
OL,19,Fhe could go home to his wife Annie
OL,20,Fafter just two days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
