OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FHe said: "They treat you with
OL,7,Fkindness, they treat you with respect.
OL,9,F"You can see that they're under
OL,10,Fpressure all the time.
OL,12,F"It must be terrible at times for
OL,13,Fthem."
OL,15,FProfessor Mohammed Munavvar, a
OL,16,Frespiratory consultant, says part of
OL,17,Fthe hospital's strategy is to
OL,18,Fencourage people to avoid being
OL,19,Fadmitted in the first place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
