OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FHe said: "That includes making sure
OL,7,Fthat the treatment for the underlying
OL,8,Fcondition is optimised, which we try
OL,9,Fand do as a team.
OL,11,F"Besides that, ensuring that they get
OL,12,Fvaccinated, because simple infections
OL,13,Fcan become more serious for people
OL,14,Fwith respiratory conditions."
OL,16,FSome patients cannot avoid a stay in
OL,17,Fthe hospital, like for Susan, 82, who
OL,18,Ffell when she had a diabetic episode.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
