OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FFive days in bed meant she needed
OL,7,Fphysiotherapy sessions to get back on
OL,8,Fher feet before she returned home.
OL,10,FShe said: "I have at least got my
OL,11,Fhusband to look after me. But all
OL,12,Fthese other people, elderly people,
OL,13,Fthat are waiting and on their own, who
OL,14,Fhave got no one to look after them,
OL,15,Fare falling between the cracks."
OL,17,FBecky Sullivan, a physiotherapist,
OL,18,Femphasised how important it is to keep
OL,19,Fmoving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
