OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,FShe said: "For older adults they can
OL,7,Flose their mobility very quickly,
OL,8,Fespecially when they're unwell.
OL,10,F"They need to use movement as
OL,11,Fmedicine, get moving, which will help
OL,12,Fthem get home sooner."
OL,14,FDischarge lounge manager Naomi Tate
OL,15,Fand her team say they have noticed
OL,16,Fvery simple solutions can make a huge
OL,17,Fdifference to the time it takes to get
OL,18,Fpatients home.
OL,20,FShe said: "We know evidence tells us
OL,21,Fthat patients recover better at home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
