OL,3,CHospital tackles bed blocking with
OL,4,Cstrategies to get patients home sooner
OL,6,F"Families and friends can help us with
OL,7,Fthis - when they come into hospital
OL,8,Fcheck - have they got outdoor clothes
OL,9,Fwith them, have they got the heating
OL,10,Fon, can they get some food in, have
OL,11,Fthey got neighbours that can help them?
OL,13,F"That will really help us speed up the
OL,14,Fdischarge process."
